transcripts:
Hi, I'm Geoffrey. 

Hi, I'm John. 

And we're from Dransfield & Ross, and we're going to give you our holiday tip for Bed Bath & Beyond. This is our lost sock sachet. And you take a lost sock and repurpose it. Fill it with pine cones where a little pine oil has been added to it. Tie it with a red ribbon, and tuck it into your sheets or towels in your linen closet, and you'll think about the holiday all year long.
